Lord Alfred of Albert.

00:21:49.434 --> 00:21:52.687 position:50% align:center
[ALFRED] Thanks.
Here's to a brighter future.

00:23:33.455 --> 00:23:35.331 position:50% align:center
[VALL D'HEBRON] What shall
we do, Sire? Any thoughts?

00:23:35.415 --> 00:23:36.458 position:50% align:center
[MARIUS]
They were slave traders?

00:23:36.541 --> 00:23:37.667 position:50% align:center
[ALFRED]
You have nothing to fear now.

00:23:37.751 --> 00:23:39.127 position:50% align:center
[SARIA]
I don't remember saying that.

00:23:39.210 --> 00:23:41.171 position:50% align:center
[ELVA] You did, because now
it's my turn to be right.

00:23:41.254 --> 00:23:43.006 position:50% align:center
[MARIUS] I can't sit
idly by--I have to act!

00:23:43.089 --> 00:23:44.424 position:50% align:center
[ALFRED]
I'm not afraid of you.

00:23:44.507 --> 00:23:46.593 position:50% align:center
